{"tid":1919080,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人個身最近成日都好痕？","createTime":"2020-03-10T14:00:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T12:19:55.000Z","uid":96536,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"bbbb9c14896b753daa9475a1193f9bc26b081f0f","tid":1919080,"uid":96536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:00:26.000Z","msg":"本身都冇咩事<br />\n係今個星期開始出現呢個問題<br />\n夜晚瞓覺一蓋住被就嚟料<br />\n啲手手腳腳好似比針吉咁<br />\n好撚痕又有少少痛<br />\n拎開張被一陣會好少少<br />\n一蓋返被又痕到仆街 瞓都瞓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n痕嘅地方有前臂手肘大小腿膝頭背脊<br />\n心口都有時會<br />\n總之就周身痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係睇返啲皮膚又冇出疹同比野咬嘅痕跡<br />\n係得自己r到紅晒<br />\n好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c2f715d550c4010b5619e883743b32a179e05bc","tid":1919080,"uid":127033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:01:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa2afecee3633e2277534bfe799a1bce08e20225","tid":1919080,"uid":96536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c2f715d550c4010b5619e883743b32a179e05bc","tid":1919080,"uid":127033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:01:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:03:02.000Z","msg":"唔好笑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c99d786f55ffb7b247d2a